tip.text: At the resto order the tapsilog. Quite good. Enjoy OJ by the bay.
Beautiful location and great view. But we got the WORST room at the resort. Room 117 by the street. Weak flush. Ugly bathroom. Tacky screen like a motel. Very shameful and puts a dent on this resort.
Loved the Korean Beef and Chicken combo here. Kimchi pretty good too.
Order the Beef Pepper Rice at the Pepper Rice Express kiosk located in the Kopitiam on L4. Try using the soy sauce mixture it's really good.
You can weigh your baggages for free. Look for these weigh scales provided by a local air carrier in the main hall before the x-ray scanners and baggage dropoff.
